beautiful acts on this show,

19:17.689 --> 19:19.324
and this is my favorite,

19:19.358 --> 19:21.793
'cause of your humility
and your raw skill.

19:21.827 --> 19:24.830
Having said all that,
it's very difficult

19:24.863 --> 19:26.999
to speak in code,
although in this case,

19:27.032 --> 19:29.868
maybe speaking English
really fast would work.

19:29.902 --> 19:31.737
But, um...

19:31.770 --> 19:35.841
because there were
so many different beats,

19:35.874 --> 19:39.244
